column5: If any one on this board that was at peterbourgh today to get tags and was in line at 815 am and when the doors opened at 830 and they told you there was no tags left. I was the guy giving the lady a hard time... if you were their please post on here as i need to know if you got a tag or not. I went to the district manager and was dealing with her, when we came back to get you guys all of you had left. either private message me or post on here .
